resolution: "ADR recorded and implemented across three author-time/runtime pairs, each kept honest by a parity/inverse relationship."
expected_result: A documented principle that runtime extension guardrails get a pure author-time counterpart.
actual_result: Decision recorded with the three established pairs and consequences; applied by pm-tlpv and pm-9ect.
